data.description: Nestled in Framingham Place subdivision, this adorable home offers the perfect blend of convenience & charm at an amazing price & a new roof! A beautiful mature tree shades the front porch, providing a serene spot to relax, it's peaceful yet close to amenities. Inside, the home is bathed in natural light, creating a welcoming atmosphere for gatherings. Just 5 minutes from Easton Town Center, Gahanna, and 10 minutes from the airport, it's also conveniently located near major highways. With a recent full roof replacement completed just last year, this home assures years of worry-free living. With its prime location and inviting features, this home is an ideal choice for first-time buyers or small families seeking a cozy retreat in a vibrant community. Washer & dryer to remain.
